
Overview of noun cleverness

The noun cleverness has 3 senses (first 1 from tagged texts)
                                     
1. (1) inventiveness, ingeniousness, ingenuity, cleverness -- (the power of creative imagination)
2. brightness, cleverness, smartness -- (intelligence as manifested in being quick and witty)
3. ingenuity, ingeniousness, cleverness -- (the property of being ingenious; "a plot of great ingenuity"; "the cleverness of its design")
